sentences: Jon Levin (born March 18, 1966) is an American musician and the current guitarist for heavy metal band Dokken.
In 1998, Levin was asked by Jeff Pilson, Dokken's bassist, to play some solos on a demo.
However, Levin did not join the group until late 2003.
When the grunge scene took over in the early 1990s, Levin took a break from being a musician because he wasn't interested in that type of music.
